%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Praggnanandhaa%E2%80%99s%20Remarkable%20First%20Act%20Sets%20the%20Stage%20for%20an%20Epic%20Journey%20in%20the%20Chess%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F22134142%2FR-Praggnanandhaa.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20type%20these%20words%2C%20the%20chess%20career%20of%20Rameshbabu%20%E2%80%9CPragg%E2%80%9D%20Praggnanandhaa%20resembles%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20first%20act%20of%20a%20biopic%20about%20a%20child%20prodigy%20destined%20for%20greatness%20and%20his%20place%20amongst%20the%20geniuses%20of%20history.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHighlights%20of%20this%20time%20are%20known%20to%20all%20those%20who%20have%20not%20been%20living%20under%20a%20rock%20the%20past%20decade%20and%20especially%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20From%20learning%20the%20game%20at%203%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20International%20Master%20of%20all%20time%20(since%20beaten)%2C%20becoming%20the%20second-youngest%20grandmaster%20of%20all%20time%20(since%20broken)%2C%20the%20youngest-ever%20to%20cross%20the%202600%20FIDE%20rating-barrier%20and%20many%2C%20many%20other%20achievements%2C%20rival%20the%20legendary%20feats%20of%20legends%20and%20biopic%20icons%20like%20Tendulkar%2C%20Federer%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9CMozart%20of%20Chess%E2%80%9D%2C%20best%20player%20of%20all%20time%20by%20universal%20opinion%2C%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20himself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFramed%20within%20this%20narrative%2C%20the%20FIDE%20World%20Cup%202023%20held%20in%20Baku%2C%20Azerbaijan%2C%20became%20the%20battleground%20of%20two%20mutually%20opposing%20biopics-in-the-making%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20month%20of%20enthralling%2C%20exciting%2C%20almost-scripted%20chess.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20the%20greatest%20player%20of%20all%20time%2C%20Carlsen%2C%20chasing%20the%20only%20trophy%20still%20missing%20from%20his%20GOAT%20cabinet%20comprising%20five%20Classical%2C%20four%20Rapid%20and%20six%20Blitz%20World-Championships.%20Pragg%2C%20the%20David%20to%20this%20Goliath%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20entered%20the%20tournament%20having%20never%20lost%20to%20Carlsen%20in%20the%20Classical%20time-format%20and%20beaten%20him%20in%20a%20series%20of%20history-making%20Rapid%20and%20Blitz%20encounters%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20player%20ever%20to%20beat%20Carlsen%20in%20the%20process.%20However%2C%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20his%20journey%20was%20devoid%20of%20the%20minor%20conflicts%20fuelling%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Pragg%2C%20trailblazer%20of%20the%20path%20his%20fellow%20child%20prodigies%20grandmasters%20Nihal%20Sarin%2C%20Arjun%20Erigaisi%2C%20and%20D.%20Gukesh%20have%20followed%2C%20had%20lagged%20slightly%20behind%20in%20FIDE%20ratings%20which%20determine%20global%20chess%20rankings%20compared%20to%20his%20peers.%20Pragg%20entered%20the%20tournament%20at%202690%20rating%20points%2C%20perilously%20close%20to%20breaking%20the%202700%20barrier%20%E2%80%93%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20double-century%20to%20a%20century%20in%20Grandmaster%20Chess%20%E2%80%93%20which%20awards%20the%20player%20the%20unofficial%20moniker%20of%20a%20Super-GM.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Gukesh%20and%20Erigaisi%20have%20already%20breached%20this%20barrier%20and%20made%20their%20ways%20into%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Top-20%20players%2C%20while%20Gukesh%2C%20the%20youngest%20of%20the%20prodigies%2C%20has%20already%20stormed%20into%20the%20top-10%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20surpass%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20in%20close%20to%20four-decades.%20To%20top%20it%20all%2C%20all%20four%20prodigies%20are%20classmates%20at%20the%20WestBridge-Anand%20Chess%20Academy%2C%20set%20up%20on%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Chess%20Schools%20of%20legend%20for%20nurturing%20chess%20talent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20cusp%20of%20turning%20into%20an%20adult%2C%20Pragg%20entered%20the%20tournament%20with%20the%20scene%20set%20for%20a%20great%20coming-of-age%20climax%2C%20seeded%2031st.%20The%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20proceeded%20in%20Baku%20as%20if%20it%20were%20written.%20A%20bye%20in%20the%20first%20round%20and%20victories%20over%20grandmasters%20Maxime%20Lagarde%20and%20David%20Navarra%20in%20the%20round%20of%2016%20went%20unremarkably%20well%2C%20like%20matches%20shown%20briefly%20with%20the%20results%2C%201.5-0.5%20in%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20favour%2C%20written%20over%20a%20scene.%20The%20highlight%20came%20on%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%2018th%20birthday%2C%20his%20initiation%20as%20an%20adult%20voting-citizen%20of%20India.%20It%20was%20akin%20to%20a%20chess%20equivalent%20of%20an%20initiation%20ritual%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20King%20Leonidas%E2%80%99%20slaying%20of%20the%20wolf%20in%20Zack%20Snyder%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E300%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0or%20Hercules%E2%80%99%20slaying%20of%20the%20Nemean%20Lion%20in%20Greek%20mythology.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPragg%20faced%20grandmaster%20Hikaru%20Nakamura%2C%20ranked%20second%20in%20the%20world%20and%20in%20the%20best%20form%20of%20his%20life%20over%20the%20past%20year%20since%202022%2C%20on%20his%2018th%20birthday%2C%20securing%20a%20draw%20in%20a%20Classical%20game%2C%20forcing%20tie-breaks%20the%20following%20day%20in%20Rapid%20and%20Blitz.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20he%20stunningly%20beat%20Nakamura%20%E2%80%93%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9CSpeed-Demon%E2%80%9D%20of%20Chess%20for%20his%20mastery%20in%20faster%20time-controls%20%E2%80%93%20in%20two%20consecutive%20games%2C%20knocking%20him%20out%20of%20the%20tournament.%20Magnus%20Carlsen%2C%20playing%20his%20own%20game%20after%20having%20narrowly%20escaped%20elimination%20by%20a%20child%20prodigy%20himself%20in%20an%20earlier%20round%2C%20got%20up%20from%20his%20ongoing%20game%20to%20congratulate%20Pragg%20upon%20the%20result%20%E2%80%93%20a%20gesture%20almost%20unheard-of%20in%20tournament%20chess.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20in%20an%20interview%20what%20he%20told%20the%20Indian%2C%20Carlsen%20repeated%20the%20mantra%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20coach%20grandmaster%20R.B.%20Ramesh%20has%20been%20telling%20anyone%20who%20will%20listen%20at%20Carlsen%E2%80%99s%20Norwegian%20camp%20for%20chess%E2%80%99s%20wunderkinds%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20him%20today%20we%20all%20want%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20like%20Pragg%E2%80%9D.%20A%20smooth%20victory%20over%20grandmaster%20Ferenc%20Berkes%20followed%20in%20the%20fifth%20round%20before%20the%20drama%20shifted%20to%20internal%20conflicts%3A%20in%20the%20quarter-finals%2C%20Pragg%20was%20to%20play%20%E2%80%9Cbest-friend%E2%80%9D%2C%20classmate%2C%20and%20compatriot%20grandmaster%20Arjun%20Erigaisi.%20The%20winner%20would%20effectively%20seal%20his%20spot%20in%20the%20Candidates%20Tournament%20to%20decide%20a%20challenger%20for%20the%20World%20Chess%20Championship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20match%20both%20players%20confessed%20to%20spending%20their%20time%20between%20matches%20hanging%20out%20with%20each%20other%2C%20discussing%20chess%2C%20and%20playing%20TT.%20They%20professed%20to%20doing%20the%20same%20on%20the%20rest%20day%20before%20their%20match%20as%20well%2C%20discussing%20everything%20except%20chess%2C%20but%20when%20the%20pieces%20aligned%20and%20the%20clock%20struck%2C%20all%20bets%20were%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArjun%20got%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20first%20Classical%20match%2C%20forcing%20Pragg%20to%20win%20on%20demand%20in%20the%20second%20Classical%20game%20the%20following%20day.%20He%20did%2C%20forcing%20tie-breaks%20which%20was%20some%20of%20the%20most%20up-and-down%20emotionally%20nerve-wracking%20chess-watching%20experience%20ever%20produced%20at%20the%20World%20Cup.%20It%20took%20nine%20games%20across%2025%20minutes%2C%2010%20minutes%2C%20and%20finally%205%20minutes%20per%20side%20where%20both%20friends%20traded%20blow-for-blow%2C%20both%20beating%20each%20other%20on%20demand%20to%20keep%20the%20match%20going%20until%20Pragg%20scored%20the%20final%20victory%2C%20finishing%20half-a-point%20ahead%2C%20through%20to%20the%20semis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20Indians%20entered%20the%20last%20eight%20of%20the%20tournament%20%E2%80%93%20the%20best%20by%20far%20India%20has%20ever%20done%2C%20the%20dawn%20of%20a%20new%20%E2%80%9Cera%20of%20youngsters%E2%80%9D%20in%20Ramesh%E2%80%99s%20words.%20When%20the%20semis%20began%2C%20Pragg%20was%20the%20lone%20survivor%2C%20the%20only%20Indian%20since%20Anand%20to%20make%20it%20this%20far.%20His%20opponent%2C%20ranked%20third%20in%20the%20world%2C%20grandmaster%20Fabiano%20Caruana%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20World-Championship%20challenger%20to%20Magnus%20himself.%20The%20match%20proceeded%20as%20their%20ratings%20would%20suggest%2C%20with%20Fabiano%20bearing%20down%20on%20Pragg%2C%20pushing%20his%20position%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20defeat%20in%20both%20Classical%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Pragg%20showed%20extraordinary%20resilience%20and%20nerve%20to%20keep%20finding%20defensive%20resources%20in%20a%20worse%20position%2C%20suffering%20for%20hours%20on%20both%20days%20in%20order%20to%20deny%20Caruana%20the%20win.%20Legends%20marveled%20at%20the%20teenager%E2%80%99s%20resiliency%2C%20and%20the%20ongoing%20come-of-age%20of%20a%20boy-wonder%20they%20were%20all%20witnessing%20on%20the%20board.%20The%20same%20pattern%20largely%20followed%20in%20shorter%20time-controls%20in%20tie-breaks%2C%20with%20Caruana%20pressing%20and%20Pragg%20forced%20to%20defend%2C%20which%20he%20did%20remarkably%20creatively%20and%20doggedly.%20The%20narrative%20flipped%20for%20just%20one%20game%20where%20Pragg%20managed%20to%20get%20an%20advantage%20with%20White%2C%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20convert%20his%20advantage%20the%20only%20time%20he%20got%20it%20in%20the%20match%2C%20knocking%20out%20another%20giant%20of%20the%20game.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20became%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20ever%20make%20it%20to%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20process.%20He%20also%20qualified%20for%20the%20Candidates%20Tournament%20%E2%80%93%20the%20only%20one%20since%20Anand%2C%20and%20the%20third-youngest%20ever%20behind%20two%20of%20the%20games%E2%80%99%20greatest%3A%20Bobby%20Fischer%20and%20Carlsen%20himself%2C%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20opponent%20in%20the%20final.%20He%E2%80%99d%20also%20crossed%20the%202700%20rating%20barrier%20by%20some%20distance%2C%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20World%20top-20%2C%20the%20lowest-seed%20ever%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20at%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Everything%20was%20set%20for%20the%20ultimate%20David%20versus%20Goliath%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEverything%20except%20Carlsen%E2%80%99s%20own%20story%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%20The%20Norwegian%2C%20who%20is%20synonymous%20in%20chess%20with%20the%20GOAT%20in%20a%20sport%20where%20other%20players%20are%20called%20demons%20and%20monsters%2C%20had%20already%20knocked%20out%20Gukesh%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20final%2C%20determined%20to%20win%20it%20as%20the%20missing%20feather%20in%20his%20bejeweled%20cap.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Carlsen%E2%80%99s%20will%2C%20as%20it%20often%20does%2C%20dictated%20the%20result.%20Despite%20Carlsen%20battling%20a%20stomach%20bug%20and%20Pragg%20drawing%20both%20Classical%20games%20to%20remain%20unbeaten%20against%20Carlsen%20in%20this%20format%2C%20Carlsen%20broke%20through%20with%20a%20win%20in%20the%20first%20game%20of%20the%20tiebreak%2C%20drawing%20the%20second%20game%20to%20finish%20half-a-point%20ahead%20as%20the%20winner%20of%20the%202023%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20end-result%2C%20this%20performance%20in%20the%20first-arc%20has%20determined%20the%20trajectory%20a%20nation%20of%20experts%20and%20fans%20alike%20expects%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20story.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%20Anand%2C%20an%20Indian%20is%20in%20the%20candidates%2C%20only%2018%20years%20old%2C%20and%20material%20for%20a%20montage%20of%20a%20nation%20proud%20and%20legends%20fawning%20can%20be%20found%20on%20virtually%20any%20news%20platform.%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20to%20Anand%20Mahindra%20%E2%80%93%20adulation%20has%20poured%20in%20from%20all%20directions.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Pragg%20wins%20around%20the%20time%20Chandrayaan%20lands%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20be%20too%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishwanathan%20Anand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fif-r-praggnanandhaa-wins-world-cup-around-the-time-chandrayaan-lands-viswanathan-anand-to-ndtv-4319102%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20evoking%20a%20nostalgia%20of%20the%20space-race%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20Bobby%20Fischer%20during%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20expectational%20narratives%20for%20Pragg%20are%20nested%20in%20the%20explosive%20narrative%20of%20the%20growth%20of%20chess%20and%20its%20budding%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20generation%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%2C%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20be%20the%20next%20dominant%20chess-power%20in%20the%20world%2C%20gifted%20with%20the%20best%20Junior%20(under%2020%20years)%20players%20in%20the%20world%20being%20mentored%20by%20former%20world%20champions%20like%20Vladimir%20Kramnik%2C%20Boris%20Gelfand%2C%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20and%20Anand%20himself%2C%20besides%20their%20personal%20coaches%20like%20Ramesh%20who%20are%20amongst%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20as%20training%20staff.%20Performances%20like%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20and%20Gukesh%E2%80%99s%20have%20inspired%20thousands%2C%20especially%20children%2C%20and%20brought%20eye-balls%20to%20chess%20on%20a%20whole%20new%20level%2C%20leading%20to%20sponsorships%20and%20increased%20access%20for%20more%20to%20play%20the%20sport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20safe%20to%20say%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20is%20set%20for%20the%20second-act%E2%80%99s%20commencement.%20For%20his%20part%2C%20Pragg%20is%20already%20off%20to%20play%20in%20his%20next%20tournament.%20A%20milestone%20has%20been%20set%20at%20the%20Candidates%20Tournament%2C%20and%20Pragg%20admits%20of%20his%20ambition%20to%20be%20world%20champion%20as%20his%20long-term%20goal%20in%20chess.%20This%20tournament%20requires%20training%20in%20a%20way%20no%20other%20tournament%20does%20in%20chess%2C%20and%20Pragg%20has%20booked%20his%20seat%20quite%20in%20advance.%20Cue%20the%20training%20montage%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20India%20better%20watch%20out%20for%20this%20sporting%20story!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbpriyaranjan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBinit%20Priyaranjan%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20masters%20in%20philosophy%20from%20St.%20Stephens%20College%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693113432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fpraggnanandhaas-remarkable-first-act-sets-the-stage-for-an-epic-journey-in-the-chess-world%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20outcome%2C%20this%20performance%20in%20the%20first%20arc%20has%20set%20the%20expectations%20of%20both%20experts%20and%20fans%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20story's%20trajectory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fpraggnanandhaas-remarkable-first-act-sets-the-stage-for-an-epic-journey-in-the-chess-world%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haiti%20gang%20opens%20fire%20on%20protesters%20in%20capital%2C%20killing%20seven%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693112321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F152B5%2Fproduction%2F_129490768_haiticop.jpg%22%2