em%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20artists%20in%20states%20across%20India%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20future%20and%20the%20preservation%20of%20traditional%20handicrafts%20as%20they%20witness%20a%20decline%20in%20interest%20among%20the%20younger%20generation%20to%20take%20over%20the%20process%20of%20work%20in%20producing%20these%20while%20maintaining%20the%20authenticity%20and%20purity%20of%20the%20craft%E2%80%99s%20indigenous%20production%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20modernisation%20and%20globalisation%20have%20taken%20centre%20stage%2C%20traditional%20crafts%20have%20experienced%20a%20loss%20of%20prestige%20and%20financial%20viability.%20Young%20people%2C%20influenced%20by%20changing%20societal%20norms%20and%20career%20opportunities%2C%20are%20increasingly%20choosing%20to%20pursue%20other%20professions%20that%20offer%20higher%20earning%20potential%20and%20greater%20social%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20in%20career%20choices%20poses%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20the%20survival%20of%20traditional%20crafts%2C%20as%20the%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%20could%20be%20lost%20forever.%20To%20counter%20this%20trend%20and%20secure%20a%20future%20for%20their%20craft%2C%20many%20artisans%20have%20taken%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20initiate%20various%20programs%20and%20initiatives%20aimed%20at%20engaging%20and%20inspiring%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmed%20Khan%2C%20an%20experienced%20exporter%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Epapier%20mache%3C%2Fem%3E%20products%2C%20expands%20on%20this%20problem%20by%20discussing%20how%20the%20state%20does%20little%20to%20provide%20better%20access%20to%20domestic%20and%20cross-border%20markets%20for%20such%20unique%20products%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20give%20you%20an%20example%20of%20our%20difficulties%2C%20a%20shipment%20of%20ours%20has%20been%20stuck%20at%20the%20borders%20of%20the%20Netherlands%20for%20the%20past%20week.%20The%20officials%20there%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20VAX%20number%2C%20which%20I%20applied%20for%20a%20month%20ago.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20help%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20end%20to%20help%2C%20instead%2C%20I%20have%20been%20making%20rounds%20to%20their%20offices%20in%20vain.%20Usually%2C%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20take%2010%20days%20to%20arrive%2C%20and%20currently%2C%20despite%20the%20delay%2C%20we%20are%20not%20being%20offered%20any%20updates.%20Now%2C%20it%20would%E2%80%99ve%20been%20different%20if%20this%20shipment%20were%20just%20about%20me%20and%20my%20needs%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not.%20I%20have%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20artists%20working%20under%20me%20whose%20households%20depend%20on%20the%20payment%20from%20this%20order.%20How%20am%20I%20supposed%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20money%20when%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20it%20myself%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20last%20generation%20of%20p%3Cem%3Eapier%20mache%3C%2Fem%3E%20artists%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exploitative%20nature%20of%20the%20relationship%20with%20exporters%20and%20the%20rising%20cost%20prices%20of%20the%20products%20gives%20more%20reasons%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20age-old%20tradition%20of%20papier%20mache%20art.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20these%20vulnerabilities%2C%20there%20is%20a%20rising%20shortage%20of%20expertise%20as%20there%20are%20very%20few%20people%20with%20indigenous%20knowledge%20of%20the%20art%20remaining%20in%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Saad*%20explains%20in%20detail%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20the%20demand%20for%20papier%20mache%20products%20has%20remained%20consistent%2C%20the%20supply%20has%20drastically%20reduced%20due%20to%20the%20dwindling%20number%20of%20artisans.%20While%20the%20prices%20of%20these%20products%20have%20not%20increased%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20raw%20materials%20has%20risen.%20Consequently%2C%20although%20papier%20mache%20pro