n%2C%20glass%2C%20and%20stainless%20steel%20products.%20Artisans%20working%20on%20these%20new%20materials%20are%20able%20to%20earn%20a%20satisfactory%20income%2C%20while%20those%20who%20remain%20dedicated%20to%20the%20original%20papier%20machie%20work%20are%20often%20dissatisfied.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20tighter%20timelines%20and%20producing%20bulk%20orders%20for%20the%20international%20market%20means%20that%20artists%20who%20can%20deliver%20on%20such%20schedules%20have%20to%20sacrifice%20quality%20in%20favor%20of%20quantity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20designs%20of%20the%20artworks%20are%20now%20dictated%20as%20per%20the%20customer%20preferences%2C%20who%20reside%20in%20international%20markets%20such%20as%20Europe%2C%20shifting%20the%20products%20from%20an%20expression%20of%20their%20cultural%20identity%20to%20ornaments%20meant%20for%20traditional%20Christian%20festivals%20like%20Christmas.%20While%20such%20orders%20are%20useful%20for%20sustaining%20their%20lives%2C%20artists%20rues%20that%20such%20changes%20have%20reduced%20the%20agency%20of%20the%20artists%20from%20their%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F2tYXRlKZRZI%3Fsi%3DV3leud4O98K13lNu%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detrimental%20effects%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20cultural%20capital%20in%20a%20rich%20kaleidoscopic%20knowledge%20and%20handicrafts%20capital%20of%20Kashmir%20are%20profound%20and%20far-reaching.%20Rapid%20commercialization%20and%20mechanization%20of%20traditional%20art%20forms%20have%20led%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20authenticity%20and%20cultural%20identity.%20As%20machines%20take%20over%20the%20production%20process%2C%20artisans%20lose%20their%20bargaining%20power%2C%20resulting%20in%20reduced%20compensations%20and%20limited%20training%20opportunities%20for%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20erosion%20of%20cultural%20knowledge%20and%20expertise%20has%20weakened%20artistic%20skills%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20unique%20cultural%20heritage.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20decline%20of%20traditional%20art%20forms%20has%20had%20severe%20economic%20consequences%20for%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20artisans%20and%20communities%20dependent%20on%20these%20crafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20decline%20of%20cultural%20tourism%20and%20educational%20impact%20further%20accentuate%20the%20need%20to%20preserve%20and%20revitalise%20traditional%20art%20forms.%20To%20safeguard%20India%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20capital%2C%20concerted%20efforts%20are%20necessary%20to%20recognise%2C%20support%20and%20promote%20these%20invaluable%20art%20forms%2C%20ensuring%20they%20continue%20to%20enrich%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20fabric%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193646%2FKMP2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193646%2FKMP2.png%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193646%2FKMP2-300x169.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20preserving%20the%20crafts%2C%20papier%20mache%20artists%20are%20making%20efforts%20to%20teach%20the%20young%20about%20the%20craft%E2%80%99s%20rich%20indigenous%20and%20cultural%20history%20which%20instills%20a%20sense%20of%20pride%20and%20appreciation%20for%20their%20craft%20among%20young%20people%20-learning%20the%20work.%20They%20organise%20workshops%2C%20training%20sessions%2C%20and%20interactive%20events%20to%20showcase%20the%20beauty%20and%20significance%20of%20traditional%20crafts.%20%C2%A0Educational%20institutions%20can%20do%20more%20to%20promote%20these%20in%20partnership%20with%20papier%20mache%20handicraft%20workshop%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20hands-on%20experiences%20and%20sharing%20stories%20about%20the%20cultural%20heritage%20behind%20each%20craft%2C%20they%20hope%20to%20reignite%20interest%20and%20curiosity%20among%20the%20youth.%20In%20addition%20to%20educational%20efforts%2C%20some%20artists%20are%20also%20exploring%20ways%20to%20make%20traditional%20crafts%20more%20relevant%20to%20contemporary%20tastes%20and%20demands.%20They%20are%20experimenting%20with%20modern%20designs%2C%20incorporating%20sustainable%20practices%2C%20and%20utilizing%20innovative%20marketing%20strategies%20to%20attract%20a%20wider%20audience%2C%20including%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20artists%E2%80%99%20commendable%20efforts%2C%20one%20major%20hindrance%20in%20their%20mission%20to%20preserve%20traditional%20crafts%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20significant%20support%20from%20the%20government.%20While%20some%20local%20and%20regional%20authorities%20may%20show%20interest%20and%20offer%20limited%20backing%2C%20a%20cohesive%20and%20nation-wide%20approach%20is%20lacking.%20Without%20substantial%20government%20support%2C%20it%20becomes%20challenging%20to%20scale%20up%20these%20initiatives%2C%20reach%20a%20larger%20audience%2C%20and%20provide%20better%20infrastructure%20for%20skill%20development%20and%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20is%20crucial%20in%20creating%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20fosters%20the%20preservation%20and%20promotion%20of%20traditional%20crafts.%20Financial%20assistance%2C%20policy%20incentives%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20development%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20encouraging%20young%20people%20to%20pur