er-mache-artisans-struggle-to-preserve-and-conserve-their-indigenous-craft%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kuber%20Group%20Director%20Gets%20A%20Call%20From%20Cops%20After%20Rolls-Royce%20Crash%20Kills%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKuber%20Group%20director%20Vikas%20Malu%20has%20been%20called%20by%20the%20Haryana%20police%20for%20questioning%20after%20Rolls-Royce%20accident%20killed%20two%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustrialist%20Vikas%20Malu%20was%20among%20the%20three%20occupants%20of%20the%20Rolls-Royce%20that%20smashed%20into%20a%20petrol%20tanker%20at%20a%20high%20speed%20earlier%20this%20week%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20three%20people%20in%20the%20tanker%20-%20the%20driver%20and%20his%20assistant%20-%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20site%20had%20shown%20little%20left%20of%20the%20Phantom%2C%20which%20costs%20over%20Rs%2010%20crore.%20The%20front%20of%20the%20car%20had%20been%20mangled%2C%20the%20engine%20was%20ablaze%20and%20the%20doors%20were%20open.%20The%20truck's%20condition%20was%20even%20worse%2C%20with%20just%20a%20heap%20of%20metal%20left%20after%20the%20blaze%20enveloped%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malu%20is%20currently%20being%20treated%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Gurugram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Nuh%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Narendra%20Bijaraniya%2C%20said%20that%20the%20entire%20stretch%20of%20the%20expressway%20is%20lined%20with%20CCTV%20cameras.%20The%20truck%2C%20he%20said%2C%20took%20a%20U-turn%20on%20the%20highway%20and%20the%20Phantom%20was%20travelling%20at%20a%20very%20high%20speed%20when%20the%20two%20collided.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693110600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F4lskedto_rolls-royce-tanker-nuh-accident_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Find