Cn%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20spacecraft%20is%20designed%20to%20provide%20remote%20observations%20of%20the%20solar%20corona%20and%20study%20the%20solar%20atmosphere%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spacecraft%20will%20extensively%20study%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fscience%2Fnews%2Fsun-observing-spacecraft-sheds-light-solar-winds-origin-4327350%5C%22%3Esolar%20winds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20disturbance%20on%20Earth%20and%20are%20commonly%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Bauroras%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20data%20from%20the%20mission%20could%20help%20better%20understand%20the%20sun's%20impact%20on%20Earth's%20climate%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20will%20the%20Aditya-L1%20mission%20launch%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satellite%20is%20ready%20and%20has%20already%20reached%20Sriharikota%2C%20but%20the%20final%20date%20for%20the%20launch%20of%20Aditya-L1%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20two%20days%2C%20ISRO%20chief%20S%20Somanath%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September%2C%20with%20the%20space%20agency%20targetting%20a%20September%202%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20far%20will%20the%20spacecraft%20travel%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aditya-L1%20will%20hitch%20a%20ride%20on%20India's%20heavy-duty%20launch%20vehicle%2C%20the%20PSLV%2C%20to%20travel%201.5%20million%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20launch%2C%20it%20will%20take%20125%20days%20from%20the%20earth%20to%20reach%20Lagrange%20point%201%20(L1).%20We%20have%20to%20wait%20till%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Somanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20head%20to%20a%20kind%20of%20parking%20lot%20in%20space%20where%20objects%20tend%20to%20stay%20put%20because%20of%20balancing%20gravitational%20forces%2C%20reducing%20fuel%20consumption%20for%20the%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20positions%20are%20called%20Lagrange%20Points%2C%20named%20after%20Italian-French%20mathematician%20Joseph-Louis%20Lagrange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20will%20the%20mission%20cost%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-capable-of-launching-more-interplanetary-missions-says-isro-chief-4332872%5C%22%3EISRO%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20earned%20a%20reputation%20for%20world-beating%20cost%20competitiveness%20in%20space%20engineering%20that%20executives%20and%20planners%20expect%20will%20boost%20its%20now-privatised%20space%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lander-shares-its-first-video-from-moons-surface-4327977%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20mission%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20became%20the%20first%20country%20to%20land%20near%20the%20South%20Pole%20of%20the%20moon.%20The%20mission%20cost%20Rs%20600%20crore%2C%20equivalent%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20blockbuster%20Bollywood%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20has%20been%20built%20at%20nearly%20half%20the%20cost%20of%20Chandrayaan-3.%20The%20government%20sanctioned%20Rs%20378%20crore%20in%202019%20for%20the%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun's%20atmosphere.%20The%20ISRO%20hasn't%20given%20an%20official%20update%20on%20costs%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693110480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fv3rk99cs_sun_625x300_27_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmoon-landing-done-india-aims-for-sun-all-we-know-about-isro-big-plan-4333032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20rover%20conducts%20experiments%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20scientists%20at%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20have%20set%20their%20eyes%20on%20their%20next%20target%20-%20the%20Sun.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%