E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20subsequent%20orders%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finternetfreedom.in%2Fmanipur-100-days-internet-shutdown%2F%5C%22%3Epartially%20lifted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20shutdown%E2%80%99s%20restrictions%20had%20little%20impact%20because%20the%20lift%20only%20targeted%20broadband%20internet%20connections.%20This%20argument%20is%20especially%20compelling%20when%20one%20considers%20that%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20users%20in%20the%20country%2C%2096%25%20to%20be%20specific%2C%20rely%20on%20mobile%20data%20connections%20to%20access%20the%20internet.%20This%20figure%20is%20based%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%2C%20and%20was%20highlighted%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Freport%2F2023%2F06%2F14%2Fno-internet-means-no-work-no-pay-no-food%2Finternet-shutdowns-deny-access-basic%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20titled%20%E2%80%9CNo%20Internet%20Means%20No%20Work%2C%20No%20Pay%2C%20No%20Food%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20was%20co-published%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20negative%20impact%20the%20shutdown%20has%20had%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20one%20has%20to%20wonder%20why%20it%20is%20still%20being%20enforced.%20Why%20would%20the%20government%20employ%20a%20method%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D3330413%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20to%20be%20ineffective%20at%20reducing%20violence%2C%20even%20after%20a%20hundred%20days%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20one%20answer%20is%20that%20shutdowns%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20in%20Manipur%2C%20serve%20only%20the%20interests%20of%20autocratic%20governments%20which%20seek%20to%20impose%20an%20information%20blackout.%20For%20months%2C%20this%20blackout%20has%20shielded%20gross%20human%20rights%20violations%20and%20served%20to%20save%20the%20face%20of%20a%20government%20that%20has%20been%20inept%20in%20dealing%20with%20what%20is%20possibly%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20worst%20human%20rights%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcentre-works-on-aid-packages-for-manipurs-displaced-in-camps-farmers-8875527%2F%5C%22%3E56%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes%20by%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20were%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20relief%20camps.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmizoram-to-disburse-humanitarian-aid-to-the-displaced-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F102881261.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20government%20of%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%2C%2013%2C000%20internally%20displaced%20people%20(IDPs)%20have%20sought%20refuge%20in%20their%20state.%20Relief%20camps%20established%20to%20house%20displaced%20communities%20continue%20to%20require%20immediate%20attention%2C%20including%20medical%20and%20sanitation%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20situations%20like%20this%2C%20it%20is%20natural%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20shutdown%20will%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20displaced%20communities%E2%80%99%20ability%20to%20access%20the%20internet.%20The%20shutdown%20prevents%20us%20from%20fully%20understanding%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20human%20rights%20crisis%2C%20and%20it%20is%20therefore%20critical%20that%20the%20government%20end%20it.%20The%20government%20can%20no%20longer%20use%20excuses%20to%20continue%20enforcing%20the%20state%20shutdown.%20Instead%2C%20it%20must%20make%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20work%20together%20with%20civil%20society%20in%20order%20to%20implement%20other%20approaches%20that%20effectively%20address%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20challenges%20without%20resorting%20to%20one%20that%20restricts%20human%20rights.%20If%20it%20is%20unable%20to%20fulfil%20this%20basic%20duty%2C%20the%20government%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20held%20acc