%2C%20where%20they%20may%20find%20out%20more%20about%20the%20position%20and%20submit%20an%20application.%20Reports%20say%20the%20feature%20will%20be%20available%20to%20premium%20users%20for%20a%20monthly%20payment%20of%20%241000%20(Rs%2082%2C300).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20hinted%20about%20introducing%20the%20feature%20in%20May.%20In%20response%20to%20a%20user's%20suggestion%20that%20Twitter%20includes%20dating%20services%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1656186902385655808%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EInteresting%20idea%2C%20maybe%20jobs%20too%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20This%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20step%20towards%20the%20platform%20becoming%20the%20everything%20app%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20previously%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20July%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F07%2F20%2Ftwitter-prepping-job-listings-feature-verified-organizations%2F%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Twitter%20made%20its%20first%20acquisition%20since%20Mr%20Musk%20bought%20the%20platform%2C%20a%20job-matching%20tech%20start-up%20named%20Laskie%20in%20May.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20acquisition%20helped%20the%20company%20in%20creating%20and%20releasing%20the%20new%20feature.%20A%20US-based%20media%20company%20WorkWeek%2C%20has%20been%20using%20the%20feature%20for%20a%20month.%20Its%20CEO%20Adam%20Ryan%20took%20to%20the%20platform%20to%20share%20the%20new%20feature%20and%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20newly%20launched%20Twitter-rival%20Threads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20there%20is%20a%20ton%20of%20hype%20around%20Zuck%20copying%20and%20pasting%20another%20app%2C%20Elon's%20Twitter%20is%20shipping%20products%20that%20make%20a%20ton%20of%20sense.%20We%20just%20got%20access%20to%20posting%20jobs%20on%20our%20company%20page.%20Considering%20we've%20hired%2020%2B%20people%20from%20Twitter%2C%20this%20is%20a%20no-brainer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20month-old%20tweet.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20also%20mentioned%20at%20that%20time%20that%20there%20was%20no%20extra%20fee%20for%20listing%20jobs%20on%20the%20company's%20profile%20and%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20the%20package%20of%20a%20paid%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693106640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F9kac2es_twitter-x-650_650x400_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-introduces-job-listing-feature-for-verified-users-4333044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20screenshot%20shared%20alongside%20the%20tweet%2C%20the%20listings%20will%20be%20placed%20under%20the%20section%20%26quot%3BWe're%20Hiring%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20is%20located%20under%20the%20bio%20of%20the%20company's%20account.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-introduces-job-listing-feature-for-verified-users-4333044%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-introduces-job-listing-feature-for-verified-users-4333044%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-introduces-job-listing-feature-for-verified-users-4333044%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scolded%20for%20excessive%20use%20of%20mobile%2C%2010-yr-old%20boy%20dies%20by%20suicide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693106117000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103099474%2Cimgsize-46148.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fguwahati%2F10-yr-old-boy-found-hanging-at-silchar-mps-residence%2Farticleshow%2F103098483.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20body%20of%20a%2010-year-old%20boy%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20domestic%20help%2C%20was%20found%20hanging%20at%20the%20resi