that%20he%20has%20been%20rewarded%20with%20a%20spot%20in%20India's%20Asia%20Cup%20squad.%20However%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20being%20selected%2C%20Varma%20might%20not%20get%20many%20chances%20in%20the%20Indian%20team's%20playing%20XI.%20The%2020-year-old%20Tilak%20has%20so%20far%20played%20seven%20T20Is%2C%20scored%20174%20runs.%20In%2025%20List%20A%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%201236%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2056.18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20is%20already%20being%20spoken%20of%20as%20a%20World%20Cup%20squad%20material%20too.%201983%20World%20Cup%20winner%20Kris%20Srikkanth%20feels%20he%20should%20not%20be%20given%20debut%20in%20big%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20give%20Tilak%20Varma%20debut%20in%20a%20big%20tournament%2C%20play%20him%20in%20the%20ODI%20series%20before%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Srikkanth%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5hEWz0kAZAY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECheeky%20Cheeka%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTilak%20has%20fantastic%20potential%2C%20a%20brilliant%20player%20-%20but%20he%20has%20to%20play%20a%20couple%20of%20one-day%20series%20before%20putting%20him%20in%20the%20WC%20squad.%20We%20need%20to%20groom%20him%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20cricketer%20and%20BCCI%20selector%2C%20Saba%20Karim%20feels%20Tilak's%20selection%20alone%20shows%20the%20confidence%20the%20selectors%20and%20team%20management%20have%20in%20him%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20the%20selectors%20and%20the%20team%20management%20can%20back%20a%20player%20after