0time%20when%20the%20wine%20industry%20is%20facing%20several%20challenges%2C%20including%20a%20decrease%20in%20wine%20demand%20due%20to%20the%20growing%20popularity%20of%20craft%20beer.%20Further%2C%20factors%20like%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20crisis%2C%20after-effects%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20and%20overproduction%20have%20also%20added%20to%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20wine-producing%20regions%20including%20Bordeaux%20and%20Languedoc%20are%20struggling%20to%20meet%20the%20expenses%20due%20to%20the%20fall%20in%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We're%20producing%20too%20much%2C%20and%20the%20sale%20price%20is%20below%20the%20production%20price%2C%20so%20we're%20losing%20money%2C''%20said%20Jean-Philippe%20Granier%2C%20from%20the%20Languedoc%20Wine%20Producers'%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20AFP%2C%20recent%20rises%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20food%20and%20fuel%2C%20linked%20to%20rocketing%20global%20energy%20prices%20and%20the%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20have%20also%20seen%20buyers%20reduce%20their%20spending%20on%20non-essential%20goods%20such%20as%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20allocated%20money%C2%A0will%20be%20used%20to%20buy%20excess%20stock%2C%20and%20the%20alcohol%20from%20destroyed%20wine%20can%20be%20sold%20to%20companies%20for%20use%20in%20items%20like%20cleansing%20products%2C%20hand%20sanitisers%2C%20perfumes%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20The%20funding%20will%20also%20be%20available%20for%20winegrowers%20to%20transition%20to%20alternative%20products%2C%20such%20as%20cultivating%20olives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20was%20''aimed%20at%20stopping%20prices%20collapsing%20and%20so%20that%20winemakers%20can%20find%20sources%20of%20revenue%20again''.%20However%2C%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Marc%20Fesneau%C2%A0stressed%20that%20the%20industry%20needed%20to%20''look%20to%20the%20future%2C%20think%20about%20consumer%20changes%20...%20and%20adapt.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistics%20from%20the%20European%20Commission%20this%20year%20till%20June%20reveal%20that%20wine%20consumption%20has%20fallen%207%20percent%20in%20Italy%2C%2010%20percent%20in%20Spain%2C%2015%20percent%20in%20France%2C%2022%20percent%20in%20Germany%2C%20and%2034%20percent%20in%20Portugal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693105320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fqadq8dng_wine_625x300_27_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrench-government-is-spending-200-million-euros-to-destroy-surplus-wine-heres-why-4333024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20of%20the%20allocated%20money%20will%20be%20used%20to%20buy%20excess%20stock%2C%20and%20the%20alcohol%20from%20destroyed%20wine%20can%20be%20sold%20to%20companies%20for%20use%20in%20items%20like%20cleansing%20products%2C%20hand%20sanitizer%2C%20and%20perfumes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrench-government-is-spending-200-million-euros-to-destroy-surplus-wine-heres-why-4333024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrench-government-is-spending-200-million-euros-to-destroy-surplus-wine-heres-why-4333024%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrench-government-is-spending-200-million-euros-to-destroy-surplus-wine-heres-why-4333024%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Location%20Managers%20Guild%20International%20Awards%20Honor%20%E2%80%98The%20Last%20of%20Us%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98John%20Wick%3A%20Chapter%204%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20Steven%20Spielberg%20Virtually%20Accepts%20Eva%20Monley%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693104904000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FThe-Last-of-Us.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235705245%22%2C%22summa