3BThe%20clearly%20orchestrated%20and%20almost%20daily%20personal%20attacks%20demonstrates%20the%20pitifully%20low%20level%20your%20government%20has%20descended%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20attacked%20his%20record%20in%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20you%20took%20office%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20the%20country%20is%20run%20by%20a%20zombie%20parliament%20where%20nothing%20meaningful%20has%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20no%20mandate%20from%20the%20people%20and%20the%20Government%20is%20adrift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResignation%20honours%20lists%2C%20in%20which%20key%20political%20allies%20of%20outgoing%20prime%20ministers%20are%20rewarded%2C%20are%20normally%20waved%20through%20by%20their%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20revenge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak's%20spokesman%20told%20reporters%20earlier%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bentirely%20untrue%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20officials%20removed%20names%20from%20Johnson's%20list%20before%20it%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20House%20of%20Lords%20vetting%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20in%20June%20over%20the%20honours%20prompted%20the%20resignation%20as%20MPs%20of%20both%20Nigel%20Adams%2C%20who%20was%20also%20omitted%20from%20the%20list%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Johnson%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%20Dorries%20announced%20her%20intention%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20observers%20have%20interpreted%20the%20resignations%20as%20Johnson's%20revenge%20on%20Sunak%20for%20forcing%20him%20out%20of%20office%20last%20July%20after%20%26quot%3BPartygate%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20string%20of%20other%20scandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20resigned%20as%20an%20MP%20claiming%20a%20stitch-up%20by%20political%20opponents%20on%20a%20cross-party%20inquiry%20probing%20whether%20he%20lied%20to%20parliament%20over%20the%20Covid%20lockdown-breaki