ia%20hoisted%20the%20flag%20on%20the%20Moon.%20From%20now%20onwards%2C%20that%20day%20will%20be%20known%20as%20National%20Space%20Day%20in%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20PM%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20I%20am%20very%20feeling%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20happiness%20among%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20beaming%20PM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20kind%20of%20happiness...%20these%20are%20very%20rare%20occasions%20when%20the%20whole%20body%20and%20soul%20is%20drenched%20in%20happiness%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20scientists%20at%20ISRO's%20Telemetry%20Tracking%20and%20Command%20Network%20Mission%20Control%20Complex%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20scientists%20had%20taken%20the%20Make%20In%20India%20initiative%20to%20the%20Moon%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20boost%20to%20indigenous%20productions%20due%20to%20Chandrayaan%203's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20he%20was%20on%20a%20two-nation%20visit%20to%20South%20Africa%20and%20Greece%20but%20his%20mind%20was%20completely%20with%20the%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20salute%20the%20scientists%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20not%20stop%20myself%20as%20I%20was%20not%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20visit%20Bengaluru%20first%20and%20meet%20our%20scientists%20right%20after%20visiting%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20the%20scientists%20cheered%20and%20broke%20into%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...I%20can%20see%20before%20my%20eyes%20every%20second%20of%20that%20day%20of%20August%2023...%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20recalling%20the%20final%2015%20challenging%20minutes%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20salute%20your%20dedication.%20I%20salute%20your%20patience.%20I%20salute%20your%20hard%20work.%20I%20salute%20your%20inspiration%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi%20as%20he%20turned%20emotional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3