%20former%20trustee%20at%20the%20museum%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpuzzling%26quot%3B%20case%20as%20curators%20typically%20consider%20themselves%20custodians%20of%20the%20artifacts%20they%20work%20with%20and%20would%20not%20steal%20or%20deface%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfascinating%20thought%26quot%3B%20that%20kleptomania%20could%20have%20spurned%20the%20thefts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20that%20as%20a%20realistic%20possibility%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20The%20Times.%20%26quot%3BYou%20do%20get%20curators%20that%20inevitably%20get%20obsessed%20%5Bwith%20the%20items%20in%20their%20departments%5D.%20I%20would%20certainly%20be%20prepared%20to%20put%20a%20mild%20bet%20on%20that%20because%20I%20can't%20see%20any%20other%20explanation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20several%20decades%2C%20as%20many%20as%202%2C000%20items%20from%20the%20museum%20are%20feared%20to%20have%20gone%20missing%2C%20been%20stolen%2C%20or%20become%20damaged%2C%20The%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Museum%20said%2C%20per%20The%20Times%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20take%20the%20issue%20of%20any%20missing%20items%20incredibly%20seriously.%20Losses%20are%20recorded%20and%20reported%20to%20the%20trustees%20on%20an%20annual%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBritish%20Museum%20director%20Hartwig%20Fischer%20said%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66621006%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20would%20step%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20his%20role%20over%20the%20scandal%2C%20admitting%20that%20the%20museum%20had%20not%20responded%20%26quot%3Bas%20comprehensively%20as%20it%20should%20have%26quot%3B%20after%20first%20being%20alerted%20to%20the%20thefts%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthief-who-plundered-british-museum-vaults-for-years-may-be-a-kleptomanic-2