y-123082600748_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-considering-inclusion-of-evs-in-priority-sector-lending-category-123082600748_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Local%20Media%20in%20Imphal%20Is%20Letting%20Biases%20Creep%20into%20Reporting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05124121%2Fimage2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20100%20days%20since%20the%20violent%20ethnic%20clash%20between%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20and%20Meitei%20communities%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%2C%20leaving%20at%20least%20170%20people%20dead%20and%20thousands%20homeless.%20While%20the%20country%20celebrated%20its%2077th%20Independence%20Day%20with%20full%20vigour%2C%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20country%20deemed%20insignificant%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be%2C%20people%20were%20buried%20in%20memories%20of%20lost%20loved%20ones%20and%20houses%20looted%20and%20burnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20must%20be%20questioned%20on%20reining%20in%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Imphal%20valley-based%20local%20media%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%20With%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20internet%20ever%20since%20the%20ethnic%20clash%20began%2C%20these%20local%20media%20groups%20have%20basically%20been%20the%20sole%20source%20of%20information%20in%20the%20valley%20and%20beyond.%20This%20calls%20for%20principled%20and%20ethical%20reporting%20that%20goes%20beyond%20one%E2%80%99s%20ethnicity.%20Did%20the%20valley-based%20local%20media%20fail%20to%20do%20so%20or%20were%20they%20able%20to%20rise%20above%20their%20own%20ethnic%20lines%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20fact-checking%20and%20an%20ethnic%20bias%20have%20resulted%20in%20several%20instances%20of%20misreporting%20that%20has%20fuelled%20the%20violence%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20protest%20in%20Churachandpur%20days%20before%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20current%20violence%2C%20a%20local%20news%20reporter%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eastmojo.com%2Fmanipur%2F2023%2F04%2F29%2Fmanipur-violence-kuki-outfit-slams-istv-over-illegal-immigrants-jab%2F%5C%22%3EISTV%20channel%20was%20seen%20referring%20to%20the%20protestors%3C%2Fa%3E%20speaking%20in%20a%20Paite%20Kuki-Zo%20dialect%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epeople%20speaking%20in%20a%20Myanmarese%20language%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20After%20furore%20from%20the%20Kuki%20Zo%20community%2C%20ISTV%20was%20quick%20to%20correct%20itself.%20While%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20isolated%20case%20before%20the%20violence%2C%20cases%20of%20misreporting%20have%20spiked%20after%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20with%20no%20accountability%20and%20course%20correction%20whatsoever%20as%20long%20as%20what%20is%20said%20fits%20a%20certain%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20week%20of%20May%2C%20which%20saw%20several%20clashes%20in%20Sugnu%20and%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20the%20local%20media%20actively%20reported%20about%20one%20side%20of%20the%20story.%20Several%20Kuki%20Zo%20villages%20were%20burnt%20down%20in%20the%20clash%20but%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F5%2F30%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-May-29-A-fierce-gun-battle-took-place-at-Leimakhong-between-Kuki-mil.html%5C%22%3Ereports%20of%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F5%2F30%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-May-29-A-fierce-gun-battle-took-place-at-Leimakhong-between-Kuki-mil.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Sangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20was%20reduced%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esome%20Kuki%20houses%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20while%20Kukis%20were%20accused%20of%20burning%20hundreds%20of%20houses%20belonging%20to%20Meiteis.%20In%20the%20early%20morning%20of%20June%209%2C%20militants%20dressed%20in%20army%20uniform%20ambushed%20Khoken%2C%20a%20Kuki%20village%20killing%2C%20three%20vil