illage%20volunteers%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20doing%20in%20a%20Kuki%20Zo%20tribal%20village%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20yet%20another%20incident%2C%20in%20a%20goodwill%20gesture%2C%20Kuki%20Zo%20volunteers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPKuTIk79VAM%5C%22%3Ehanded%20over%20five%20Meitei%20civilians%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Jat%20Regiment%2C%20but%20the%20same%20gesture%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-five-civilians-rescued-from-kuki-militants%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-five-civilians-rescued-from-kuki-militants%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E4%20AR%20personnels%20and%2020%20JAT%20successfully%20rescued%205%20Meitei%20civilians%20who%20were%20abducted%20by%20Kuki%20miscreants%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20On%20a%20July%2023%20incident%20in%20the%20Bishnupur-Churachandpur%20bordering%20area%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F7%2F24%2FOur-CorrespondentMoirang-Jul-23-Kuki-militants-led-by-hundreds-of-women-purportedly-as-human-shields-ha.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F7%2F24%2FOur-CorrespondentMoirang-Jul-23-Kuki-militants-led-by-hundreds-of-women-purportedly-as-human-shields-ha.html%5C%22%3E%20was%20seen%20misreporting%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20incident%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKuki%20militants%20with%20hundreds%20of%20their%20associates%E2%80%A6%20and%20set%20the%20Children%20Treasure%20High%20School%20on%20fire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20An%20impartial%20report%20on%20the%20same%20incident%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmanipur-horror-school-torched-1-shot-in-fresh-violence-chances-of-returning-to-classrooms-bleak%2Farticleshow%2F102061589.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentions%20that%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20school%20was%20Liankhothang%20Vaiphei%2C%20a%20Kuki%20Zo%20individual.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20absurd%20to%20think%20someone%20would%20burn%20his%20own%20school%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20case%20of%20fabricated%20reporting%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fclash-between-kukis-and-paites-in-churachandpur%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fclash-between-kukis-and-paites-in-churachandpur%5C%22%3E%20on%20August%2013%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EA%20deadly%20clash%20reportedly%20broke%20out%20between%20Kuki%20and%20Paite%20militants%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20such%20incident%20and%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20also%20had%20to%20release%20a%20statement%20refuting%20such%20fabricated%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20a%20few%20of%20the%20countless%20instances%20of%20half-truths%20and%20misreporting%20by%20the%20Imphal-based%20local%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20few%20instances%20of%20biased%20reporting%20are%20already%20doing%20enough%20harm%2C%20little%20do%20we%20realise%20the%20wider%20negative%20implications%20of%20such%20reports%20that%20get%20published%20without%20fact-checking.%20I%20want%20to%20highlight%20one%20instance%20with%20a%20much%20larger%20implication%2C%20in%20which%20several%20Imphal-based%20local%20media%20groups%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fe-pao.net%2FGP.asp%3Fsrc%3D27..050823.aug23%23%3A~%3Atext%3DImphal%252C%2520August%252004%25202023%253A%2520The%2CKuki%2520war%2520happened%2520in%2520Manipur.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EE-Pao%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F8%2F5%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Aug-4-Young-climate-activist-Licypriya-Kangujam-has-claimed-that-there-is-no.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Sangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstory.poknapham.in%2Fposts%2F64ceb12fd741d9891edc37ae%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20People%E2%80%99s%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20seem%20to%20have%20taken%20at%20face%20value%20a%20Facebook%20post%20dated%20August%204%20from%20a%20climate%20activist%2C%20Licypriya%20Kangujam.%20The%20post%20claims%20the%20activist%20has%20gotten%20an%20RTI%20reply%20regarding%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAnglo%20Kuki%20War%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20filed%20on%20June%2017%2C%202023.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20the%20account%20holder%20has%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EI%20filed%20an%20RTI%20under%20RTI%20Act%202005%E2%80%A6%20to%20clear%20doubts%20on%20the%20fake%20Anglo-Kuki%20war.%20There%20is%20no%20such%20incident%20happened%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EE-Pao%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20the%20same%20social%20media%20post%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%20in%20response%20to%20an%20RTI%20application%2C%20has%20stated%20that%20no%20Anglo-Kuki%20war%20occurred%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%A6%20Out%20of%20the%2062%2C%20there%20are%20only%20four%20freedom%20fighters%20from%20Kuki%20community%20who%20received%20pension%20scheme%20of%20MHA%20called%20Samman%20Pension%20under%20Swatantrata%20Sainik%20Samman%20Yojana%20(SSSY).%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20After%20further%20research%20and%20fact%20checking%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20RTI%20reply%20had%20told%20the%20applicant%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20MHA%20website%20for%20the%20SSSY%20pension%20beneficiary%20list%20for%20freedom%20fighters.%20While%20there%20were%2062%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20SSSY%20list%20up%20to%20September%2030%2C%202010%20for%20which%20there%20is%20no%20further%20information%20on%20each%20beneficiary%2C%20there%20is%20in%20fact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mha.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FUpdatedlistofSSSYBeneficiaries_04022022.pdf%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20list%20from%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20there%20are%2013%20active%20SSSY%20beneficiaries%20from%20Manipur%2C%2011%20of%20whom%20belong%20to%20the%20Kuki%20Zo%20community%20and%20not%20four%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20Imphal-based%20local%20media.%20With%20regards%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAnglo%20Kuki%20war%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20though%20there%20are%20disagreements%20on%20whether%20to%20call%20it%20a%20war%20or%20a%20rebellion%2C%20it%20certainly%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20fake%20event%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20local%20media.%20The%20RTI%20reply%20does%20not%20contain%20information%20specific%20to%20the%20Anglo%20Kuki%20war%20(it%20is%20typical%20for%20RTIs%20to%20furnish%20incomplete%20information)%20and%20it%20certainly%20does%20not%20say%20it%20did%20not%20happen.%20Records%20of%20the%20same%20can%20be%20found%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%2C%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20one%20can%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famritmahotsav.nic.in%2Fdistrict-reopsitory-detail.htm%3F17827%5C%22%3Efind%20mention%20of%20names%20of%20freedom%20fighters%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famritmahotsav.nic.in%2Fdistrict-reopsitory-detail.htm%3F12809%5C%22%3EEnjakhup%20Khollou%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famritmahotsav.nic.in%2Funsung-heroes-detail.htm%3F12299%5C%22%3EChengjapao%20Doungel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famritmahotsav.nic.in%2Fdistrict-reopsitory-detail.htm%3F11509%5C%22%3EMangpithang%20Kipgen%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20several%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourcing%20information%20from%20social%20media%20without%20fact-checking%2C%20such%20as%20in%20the%20instance%20above%2C%20has%20several%20negative%20implications.%20It%20has%20been%20found%20that%20on%20certain%20digital%20platforms%20like%20Wikipedia%2C%20such%20unfounded%20local%20media%20reports%20have%20been%20included%20as%20citations%20to%20shape%20the%20narrative%20according%20to%20certain%20vested%20interests.%20The%20Wikipedia%20page%20for%20the%20said%20event%20has%20recently%20been%20edited%20numerous%20times%20based%20on%20these%20local%20media%20reports%20that%20are%20often%20untrue.%20A%20systemic%20reshaping%20of%20narratives%20is%20made%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20digital%20literacy%20in%20certain%20disadvantaged%20communities.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20becomes%20pertinent%20to%20understand%20the%20wider%20repercussions%20of%20such%20irresponsible%20reporting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20is%20that%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKuki%20militants%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20came%20in%20vogue%20with%20the%20current%20ethnic%20clash%20in%20Manipur%2C%20whereby%20the%20local%20media%20have%20resorted%20to%20the%20mass%20branding%20of%20all%20Kuki%20Zo%20village%20defence%20volunteers%20as%20Kuki%20militants.%20The%20Kuki%20Zos%20have%20accused%20the%20Meiteis%20of%20mass%20branding%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eillegal%20immigrants%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epoppy%20cultivators%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20so%20on.%20While%20there%20can%20be%20certain%20anomic%20elements%20who%20might%20label%20a%20community%20based%20on%20stereotypes%20or%20narratives%20of%20those%20in%20power%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20valley-based%20local%20media%20in%20mass%20branding%20a%20community%20makes%20one%20question%20why%20they%20are%20not%20fulfilling%20their%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20media%20is%20the%20only%20source%20of%20information%20for%20the%20many%20in%20Manipur%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20valley.%20If%20these%20organisations%20demonise%20a%20certain%20community%2C%20it%20will%20make%20peace%20harder%20to%20achieve.%20Instead%2C%20projecting%20the%20sufferings%20and%20misdeeds%20of%20both%20communities%20can%20help%20readers%20and%20viewers%20introspect%20and%20get%20the%20dice%20rolling%20for%20societal%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EL.%20Anthony%20Doungel%20is%20a%20techie%20working%20at%20an%20MNC%2C%20often%20engrossed%20in%20sociopolitics%20to%20pass%20the%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693060227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05124121%2Fimage2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fthe-local-media-in-imphal-is-letting-biases-creep-into-reporting%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Misrepresentation%20of%20the%20conflict%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20fact-checking%20has%20wider%20repercussions%20and%20can%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20ensuring%20peace%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fthe-local-media-in-imphal-is-letting-biases-creep-into-reporting%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20Moves%20to%20Withhold%20Posts%20on%20UP%20Teacher%20Getting%20Muslim%20Boy%20Slapped%2C%20Little%20Done%20to%20Charge%20Teacher%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F27181809%2Ftwitter-censor.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUsers%20on%20social%20media%2C%20expressing%20horror%20over%20the%20organised%20slapping%20of%20a%20Muslim%20child%20by%20his%20classmates%20by%20his%20teacher%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20learnt%20that%20their%20tweets%20(posts%20on%20X)%20had%20been%20blocked%20by%20a%20government%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20prominent%20users%20complained%20of%20their%20tweets%20being%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTwitterIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40TwitterIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20explain%20what%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20in%20this%20tweet%20that%20warrants%20blocking%20in%20India%3F%20Speaking%20about%20the%20trauma%20of%20a%20child%20is%20a%20crime%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJin8h