wp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26191219%2Fimages-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOfficials%20at%20TRIFED%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Tribal%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Development%20Federation%20of%20India%20Limited%2C%20a%20cooperative%20body%20associated%20with%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Tribal%20Affairs%20%E2%80%93%20earlier%20this%20year%20stayed%20away%20from%20a%20meeting%20called%20by%20the%20body%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20with%20two%20RSS-affiliated%20organisations%2C%20Akhil%20Bhartiya%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%20and%20Sahakar%20Bharati%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frss-bodies-politics-trifed-8907902%2Flite%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20at%20the%20Federation%20%E2%80%93%20Amit%20Bhatnagar%2C%20General%20Manager%2C%20TRIFED%20%E2%80%93%20had%20responded%20to%20TRIFED%20chairman%20Ramsinh%20Rathwa%E2%80%99s%20note%20on%20March%2023%20asking%20him%20and%20other%20officials%20to%20be%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%20by%20saying%20that%20Rathwa%20was%20asking%20for%20the%20cooperative%20staff%E2%80%99s%20presence%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a%20meeting%20of%20organisations%20with%20political%20aspect%E2%80%9D.%20This%2C%20Bhatnagar%20said%2C%20was%20against%20service%20rules%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%2C%20inter-alia%2C%20provide%20that%20every%20government%20servant%20shall%2C%20at%20all%20times%2C%20maintain%20political%20neutrality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatnagar%20added%20that%20it%20was%20incumbent%20upon%20officials%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20only%20to%20maintain%20political%20neutrality%20but%E2%80%A6also%20appear%20to%20do%20so%E2%80%A6and%20not%20subscribe%20in%20aid%20of%2C%20or%20assist%20in%20any%20other%20manner%20in%20this%20regard%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20meeting%20took%20place%20on%20March%2028%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20only%20Rathwa%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20BJP%20MP%20%E2%80%93%20was%20present%20from%20TRIFED.%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%E2%80%99s%20main%20liaison%20with%20the%20government%2C%20Sharad%20Chavan%2C%20and%20Sahakar%20Bharati%20national%20president%20D.N.%20Thakur%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting%20reflected%20discussions%20about%20potential%20collaborations%20between%20TRIFED%20and%20the%20two%20organisations%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20described%20as%20NGOs%20engaged%20in%20social%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chavan%20and%20Thakur%20learnt%20of%20Bhatnagar%E2%80%99s%20description%20of%20their%20organisations%20as%20%E2%80%98political%E2%80%99%20they%20reportedly%20objected%2C%20and%20demanded%20the%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20June%2030%2C%20the%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%20sent%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20TRIFED%20Managing%20Director%20Gupta%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cwrongly%20presumed%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Ca%20political%20organisation%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20demanding%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20March%2024%20letter%20by%20Bhatnagar%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20%E2%80%9COn%20July%2024%2C%20Chavan%20wrote%20to%20Union%20Tribal%20Affairs%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20TRIFED%20letter%20%E2%80%9Ctarnishes%20our%20nationwide%20image%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanding%20a%20probe%20and%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20persons%20responsible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2022%2C%20Bhatnagar%20reportedly%20wrote%20to%20Rathwa%20and%20said%20his%20earlier%20letter%20%E2%80%9Cseems%20to%20have%20caused%20miscommunication%20and%20should%20be%20withdrawn%20with%20immediate%20effect%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20aforesaid%20letter%20stands%20withdrawn%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rathwa%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20dispute%20%E2%