0link%20on%20my%20phone.%20I%20was%20suspicious.%20I%20then%20opened%20it%20on%20my%20laptop%20so%20I%20could%20click%20around%20and%20make%20sure%20it%20was%20actually%20the%20USPS.%20I%20am%20a%20prudent%20internet%20user%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20legit.%20It%20linked%20to%20a%20page%20about%20%26quot%3Binformed%20delivery%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20%3Cem%3Eam%3C%2Fem%3E%20an%20Informed%20Delivery%20subscriber.%20I%20like%20to%20know%20when%20my%20late-night%20Halloween%20decor%20purchases%20are%20arriving%20before%20they%20hit%20my%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20had%20a%20tracking%20number%2C%20an%20FAQ%20page%2C%20and%20other%20indicators%20that%20left%20me%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20back%20to%20my%20phone%2C%20entered%20my%20home%20address%20%E2%80%94%20which%20in%20retrospect%20I'm%20not%20sure%20why%20they'd%20need%20that%20%E2%80%94%20my%20email%20address%2C%20and%20my%20phone%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20red%20flag%20that%20trumps%20all%20red%20flags%20appeared%3A%20it%20asked%20me%20for%20my%20credit%20card%20information%20for%20a%20%24o.30%20redelievery%20fee.%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%94%20this%20doesn't%20feel%20right%2C%20but%20what%20the%20hell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWELP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20it%20prompted%20me%20to%20enter%20the%20verification%20code%20it%20sent%20to%20my%20phone.%20It%20also%20had%20a%20timer%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20got%20a%20code.%20After%20checking%20all%20my%20spam%20folders%20to%20make%20sure%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20HAD%20BEEN%20GOT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWith%20a%20heart%20full%20of%20shame%2C%20I%20reported%20the%20scam%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221582%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shame%20lady%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e66b2d912f290019aa0922%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20am%20ashamed.%3Cp%3EHaven%20Orecchio-Egresitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20called%20my%20husband%2C%C2%A0a%20web%20developer%20who%20also%20works%20in%20IT.%20You%20know%2C%20that%20sassy%20department%20that%20sends%20you%20scathing%20emails%20warning%20you%20not%20to%20fall%20for%20phishing%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20displeased.%20And%20also%2C%20not%20quite%20as%20surprised%20as%20I%20was%20that%20I%20could%20fall%20for%20something%20like%20this.%20I'm%20offended%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20tried%20to%20call%20the%20bank%20to%20report%20fraud.%20That%20call%2C%20however%2C%20was%20interrupted%20by%20their%20call.%20The%20bank%20had%20detected%20fraud%20and%20was%20already%20letting%20him%20know%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cancelled%20the%20card%20and%20no%20money%20was%20lost%20%E2%80%94%20that%20we%20know%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20let%20my%20IT%20department%20know%20because%20I%20opened%20the%20link%20on%20my%20work%20laptop.%20(Please%20don't%20fire%20me.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20began%20Googling%20everything%20about%20the%20USPS%20scam.%20I%20should%20have%20trusted%20my%20gut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20USPS%20says%20they%20don't%20send%20tracking%20texts%20or%20emails%20with%20links%20in%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uspis.gov%2Fnews%2Fscam-article%2Fsmishing-package-tracking-text-scams%5C%22%3EUSPS%20has%20an%20entire%20webpage%20warning%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20%26quot%3Bsmishing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20name%20for%20scams%20conducted%20via%20text%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222130%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22smishing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e645c94c17ff0019bb390b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20USPS%20warns%20about%20smishing.%20What%20a%20stupid%20name.%3Cp%3EHaven%20Orecchio-Egresitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USPS%20does%20have%20services%20to%20track%20packages%2C%20but%20you'd%20have%20to%20ask%2