rnment%2C%20three%20teams%20have%20reached%20Manipur%2C%20and%20five%20teams%20will%20arrive%20soon.%20These%20teams%20will%20provide%20health%20facilities%20in%20Moreh%2C%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%20areas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%2035%20people%20have%20already%20died%20in%20Churachandpur%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20medicines%20and%20proper%20treatment%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20the%20district%2C%20according%20to%20Kuki%20Khanglai%20Lawmpi%2C%20a%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20organisation%20that%20has%20been%20providing%20medical%20aid%20in%20relief%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20have%20died%20since%20May%203%2C%20but%20what%20about%20those%20who%20could%20have%20survived%20if%20the%20government%20had%20provided%20them%20with%20proper%20treatment%20and%20medication%3F%20Then%20many%20could%20have%20survived.%20In%20the%20past%203.5%20months%2C%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20anyone%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20helping%20out%20in%20our%20relief%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20K.%20Haokip%2C%20information%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Khanglai%20Lawmpi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaokip%20further%20added%20that%20many%20have%20died%20because%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20reach%20Imphal%20%E2%80%93%20where%20they%20could%20get%20proper%20treatment%20in%20bigger%20hospitals%20like%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(JNIMS)%20and%20Regional%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(RIIMS).%20%E2%80%9COn%20Monday%20(August%2021)%2C%20a%20person%20died%20of%20typhoid%20because%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20proper%20medicines%20and%20machines%20to%20treat%20him.%20Two%20people%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20their%20cancer%20treatment%2C%20and%20a%20few%20died%20from%20malaria%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haokip%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaokip%20is%20looking%20after%2063%20relief%20camps%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20housing%209%2C000%20people%2C%20and%20another%205%2C000%20staying%20in%20private%20houses.%20He%20believes%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20the%20Kuki%20community%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20people%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20where%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20sending%20doctors%20from%20AIIMS%20Guwahati%20on%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kimjaneng%2C%20secretary%20of%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Environment%20and%20Economic%20Development%20Services%20(FEEDS)%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMedicines%20are%20always%20in%20short%20supply.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20displaced%20have%20to%20purchase%20it%20themselves.%20Due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20medical%20infrastructure%2C%20patients%20with%20serious%20issues%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20Kohima%2C%20Dimapur%20and%20Gauhati%20for%20treatment%20by%20the%20medical%20team%20of%20the%20relief%20committee%2C%20which%20is%20very%20expensive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kangpokpi%2C%20according%20to%20FEEDS%2C%2010%20people%20died%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20medicine%20and%20improper%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170310%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-26-at-4.34.21-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170310%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-26-at-4.34.21-PM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170310%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-26-at-4.34.21-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670005%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWall%20of%20Remembrance%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Kuki%20community%20with%20100%20coffins%20and%20pictures%20of%2