C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170157%2FScreenshot-2023-08-26-at-5.01.44-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170157%2FScreenshot-2023-08-26-at-5.01.44-PM-300x212.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170157%2FScreenshot-2023-08-26-at-5.01.44-PM-1024x724.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670004%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKuki%20students%20protesting.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20they%20approached%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Manipur%20on%20June%2026%20and%20demanded%20alternative%20arrangements%2C%20specifically%20transferring%20students%20to%20other%20engineering%20institutes%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20students%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20governor%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Zemin%20Haokip%2C%20a%20second-year%20student%20of%20NIT%20Manipur%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CStarting%20our%20studies%20from%20some%20other%20university%20is%20also%20impossible%20for%20us.%20We%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20further%20chances%20to%20get%20into%20NIT%2C%20IIT%2C%20and%20IIIT%2C%20etc.%2C%20which%20take%20admission%20through%20JEE.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20pursue%20another%20course%2C%20or%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20each%20one%20of%20us%20will%20think%20of.%20In%20this%20situation%2C%20the%20only%20option%20for%20us%20is%20a%20college%20transfer%2C%20but%20for%20that%20the%20government%20must%20listen%20to%20our%20concern%2C%20the%20dean%20must%20reply%20to%20students.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaul%2C%20an%20engineering%20student%2C%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20is%20what%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eachche%20din%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20looks%20like%20then%20I%20shudder%20to%20think%20how%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ebure%20din%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20will%20be.%20Offline%20classes%20for%20some%20while%20sidelining%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20students%20of%20the%20state%2C%20is%20this%20also%20part%20of%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20T.%20Haokip%2C%20who%20is%20the%20education%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Students%E2%80%99%20Organisation%20(KSO).%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20in%20touch%20with%20multiple%20universities%20so%20that%20our%20students%20can%20continue%20their%20studies%2C%20and%20so%20far%2C%20only%20Kannur%20University%2C%20which%20is%20in%20Kerala%2C%20has%20given%20us%20the%20green%20signal%20for%20our%20students%20to%20continue%20their%20studies%20there.%20We%20are%20looking%20for%20other%20options%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealso%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20is%20not%20demanding%20online%20classes%20from%20institutes%20in%20Manipur.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20get%20internet%20%5Baccess%5D%20is%20not%20easy%20for%20every%20student%2C%20and%20students%20have%20to%20go%20and%20sit%20in%20the%20DC%20office%20for%20their%20studies%2C%20which%20I%20believe%20is%20useless%20for%20students%20who%20are%20pursuing%20medical%20and%20engineering%20because%20for%20these%20two%20subjects%2C%20practical%20knowledge%20is%20more%20important%20than%20theories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHousing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%2070%2C000%20people%20are%20living%20in%20relief%20camps%20in%20Manipur%20and%20for%20them%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20had%20promised%20temporary%20housing.%20Only%20a%20few%20houses%20in%20eastern%20Imphal%20were%20inaugurated%20by%20%C2%A0chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20(August%2022)%2C%20while%20in%20other%20districts%2C%20construction%20is%20still%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20all%20basic%20amenities%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20food%20and%20medical%20care%2C%20were%20being%20provided%20to%20those%20living%20in%20relief%20camps.%20However%2C%20those%20working%20on%20the%20ground%20say%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealso%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20of%20the%20relief%20camps%20in%20Imphal%20Naorem%20Birahari%20College%2C%20where%20more%20than%20300%20people%20are%20living.%20The%20residents%20of%20the%20relief%20camps%20get%20400%20grams%20of%20food%20per%20person%20per%20day%20from%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20food%20we%20get%20is%20not%20enough%20for%20the%20people%20living%20here%2C%20but%20somehow%20we%20are%20managing%20as%20many%20volunteer%20organisations%20have%20donated%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajeshwar%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETravel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20the%20Kuki%20community%20is%20unable%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20valley%20while%20the%20Meiteis%20are%20unable%20to%20access%20the%20hill%20areas.%20To%20ensure%20airport%20access%20for%20those%20living%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20Shah%20had%20promised%20helicopter%20services%20to%20the%20Imphal%20airport.%20The%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(CoTU)%20chairman%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20service%20is%20yet%20to%20start%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20while%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20Ginza%20Vualzong%2C%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20spokesperson%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20civilian%20will%20dare%20to%20use%20that%20service%20to%20reach%20the%20airport%20because%20if%20we%20do%20then%20we%20will%20be%20killed%20in%20Imphal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693051254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170436%2FScreenshot-2023-08-26-at-5.04.26-PM.png%22%2C%22originI