irected%20by%20the%20very%20talented%20Neeraj%20Ghaywan%2C%20a%20Dalit%20himself%2C%20who%20made%20a%20courageous%20move%20by%20portraying%20a%20Buddhist%20wedding%20on%20a%20mainstream%20global%20streaming%20platform.%20Prior%20to%20this%20collaboration%20with%20the%20elites%20of%20the%20Hindi%20cinema%20scene%2C%20he%20has%20given%20viewers%20hard-hitting%20stories%20that%20delve%20into%20complex%20subjects%20such%20as%20caste%2C%20patriarchy%2C%20sexuality%20and%20love%20in%20the%20most%20poignant%2C%20authentic%20and%20sensitive%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhaywan%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMasaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EGeeli%20Pucchi%3C%2Fem%3E%20take%20us%20through%20journeys%20of%20lives%20of%20unseen%2C%20invisible%20individuals%2C%20such%20as%20Deepak%20Kumar%2C%20a%20young%20man%20with%20aspiration%2C%20helping%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20caste-based%20occupation%20of%20burning%20pyres%20for%20the%20dead%20in%20the%20ghats%20of%20Varanasi%2C%20and%20Bharati%20Mondal%2C%20a%20queer%20labourer%20asserting%20herself%20in%20the%20world%20of%20upper%20castes%20and%20men.%20These%20characters%20are%20humanised%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20you%20can%20see%20the%20director%20has%20placed%20a%20piece%20of%20himself%20into%20the%20narratives.%20Before%20writing%20anything%20else%2C%20I%20must%20acknowledge%20that%20being%20the%20only%20vocal%20Dalit%20director%20in%20the%20Hindi%20film%20industry%20must%20not%20be%20easy.%20One%20must%20feel%20isolated%20and%20Ghaywan%20has%20been%20able%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20space%20for%20himself%20through%20the%20challenges%20of%20an%20industry%20that%20heavily%20relies%20upon%20kinship%20networks%20and%20the%20goodwill%20of%20%E2%80%98family%20friends%E2%80%99.%20Ghaywan%E2%80%99s%20current%20creative%20work%20for%20MIH%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20a%20long%20creative%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20347px)%2085vw%2C%20347px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F