crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20launched%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20scheme%20at%20Tirukkuvalai%20in%20Nagapattinam%2C%20where%20his%20father%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20M.%20Karunanidhi%20had%20studied.%20Stalin%20also%20shared%20the%20meal%20with%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20expanded%20the%20scheme%20considering%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20preliminary%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20children%20attend%20school%20without%20hunger%20and%C2%A0prevent%20malnutrition%2C%20achieve%20average%20height%20in%20children%2C%20prevent%20underweight%20in%20adolescents%2C%20prevent%20anemia%20and%20vitamin%20B12%20deficiency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStalin%20had%20invited%20elected%20representatives%20to%20launch%20the%20plan%E2%80%99s%20extension%20in%20a%20government%20primary%20school%20in%20their%20respective%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20CM%20MK%20Stalin%20enjoys%20a%20meal%20with%20school%20children%20in%20Nagapattinam%20district%20as%20he%20launched%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20breakfast%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20was%20initially%20launched%20to%20provide%20breakfast%20to%20over%201%20lakh%20students%20in%20classes%201%20to%205%20across%201%2C545%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAc7KBSI4uF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAc7KBSI4uF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1694908221876531270%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmiles%20all%20around%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20minister%20Ma%20Subramanian%20inaugurated%20the%20programme%20at%20the%20Chennai%20Primary%20School%20at%20Manthope%20in%20Saidapet.%20As%20many%20as%201%2C075%20students%20of%20the%20school%20will%20benefit%20from%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20stated%20that%20each%20student%20will%20be%20served%20cereals%20like%20semolina%2C%20wheat%2C%20rice%2C%20millet%2C%20and%20pulses%2C%20and%20locally%20available%20vegetables%20from%20Monday%20to%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20be%20provided%20150%20to%20200%20grams%20of%20cooked%20food%20and%2060%20grams%20of%20sambar%20with%20vegetables.%20This%20is%20apart%20from%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20provided%20to%20students%20till%20Class%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Paul%20Raj%2C%20a%20fifth-grade%20student%20at%20Chennai%20Primary%20School%20in%20Saidapet%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20used%20to%20attend%20school%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach%2C%20since%20his%20mother%20has%20to%20leave%20for%20work%20early%20and%20family%20has%20limited%20resources.%20On%20Friday%2C%20his%20face%20lit%20up%20when%20the%20school%20bell%20rang%2C%20announcing%20the%20breakfast%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20he%20had%20a%20satisfying%20meal%20of%20khichdi%2C%20sambar%20and%20kesari.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20would%20be%20famished%20by%2011%20am%20and%20eagerly%20wait%20for%20the%20bell%20to%20ring%20to%20have%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20provided%20at%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20child%20grinned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%2070%25%20of%20the%20students%20do%20not%20have%20breakfast%20at%20home.%20We%20were%20happy%20that%20the%20students%20enjoyed%20the%20breakfast.%20No%20one%20wasted%20the%20food.%20The%20dull%2C%20inactive%20faces%20of%20the%20children%20lit%20up%20with%20happiness%2C%E2%80%9D%20V.%20Umaparvathy%20at%20the%20Saidapet%20school%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%